---
import GlassCard from '../ui/GlassCard.astro';
import BeforeAfterMockup from '../ui/BeforeAfterMockup.astro';
---

<section id="social-proof" class="section-social section-fade-top section-fade-bottom" style="--fade-from: #010101;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title scroll-animate"><span class="text-neon">Resultados</span> falam mais que qualquer promessa</h2>
      <ul class="section-subtitle-list scroll-animate delay-100">
        <li>✓ Mais mensagens no WhatsApp</li>
        <li>✓ Mais pedidos de orçamento</li>
        <li>✓ Mais <span class="text-neon">clientes</span> entrando todos os dias</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mockup-container scroll-animate delay-150">
      <BeforeAfterMockup />
    </div>

    <div class="proof-grid">
      <!-- Depoimento 1 -->
      <GlassCard class="scroll-animate delay-200">
        <div class="proof-author">
          <div class="avatar-placeholder placeholder-0">RA</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <h4>Roberto Almeida</h4>
            <span>CEO, TechGrowth</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="proof-text">"Nossas conversões dobraram na primeira semana após o lançamento. O design e a velocidade da página são absurdos."</p>
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      </GlassCard>

      <!-- Depoimento 2 (Simulado) -->
      <GlassCard class="scroll-animate delay-300">
        <div class="proof-author">
          <div class="avatar-placeholder placeholder-1">MC</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <h4>Mariana Costa</h4>
            <span>Mentora de Vendas</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="proof-text">"Sempre sofri com sites lentos que perdiam clientes no meio do caminho. A OCARECADEV resolveu isso e entregou uma verdadeira máquina de vendas."</p>
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      </GlassCard>

      <!-- Depoimento 3 (Simulado) -->
      <GlassCard class="scroll-animate delay-400">
        <div class="proof-author">
          <div class="avatar-placeholder placeholder-2">CM</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <h4>Carlos Moura</h4>
            <span>Sócio, Agência XYZ</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="proof-text">"Ter um código limpo e analytics injetado certinho nos botões me economizou muito tempo. O tracking funciona perfeitamente."</p>
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      </GlassCard>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-social {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    position: relative;
    background-color: #010101;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .section-social {
      padding: 6rem 0;
    }
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0 1rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }
  }

  .section-subtitle-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .section-subtitle-list {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }

  .mockup-container {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    padding: 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .proof-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .proof-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .proof-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .avatar-img {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary-neon);
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .avatar-placeholder {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--glass-border);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary, #ffffff);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .placeholder-0 {
    background: linear-gradient(to top right, #00FF9D, #00663d);
    border-color: #00E58B;
  }

  .placeholder-1 {
    background: linear-gradient(to top right, #3b82f6, #7c3aed);
    border-color: #00A666;
  }

  .placeholder-2 {
    background: linear-gradient(to top right, #4ade80, #3b82f6);
  }

  .author-info h4 {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .author-info span {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .proof-text {
    color: #e5e5e5;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .stars {
    color: var(--color-primary-neon);
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }


